---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Paragraph from "../components/Paragraph.astro";
import Pager from "../components/Pager.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Heading level={1}>Humans</Heading>
  <Paragraph>
    Every human being has something to learn from, here are a few I love.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Lex Fridman, for his relentless exploration of the human condition and
    bringing countless hours of insightful conversations into the world.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Ed Sheeran, for showing that hard work can get you anywhere and being an
    absolute master in his craft of songwriting and, above all, performing.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Kobe Bryant, for embodying unparalleled dedication. Also, for showing that
    when you put a dot after a great story, it is up to you to write the next
    chapter.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Hasan Minhaj, for being a hilarious storyteller and the reason for numerous
    laughs.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Elon Musk, for coming up with ridiculous ideas and then actually making them
    happen.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    Neil deGrasse Tyson, for manifesting the beauty of science, logical
    reasoning and the universe.
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>&lt;3</Paragraph>
  <Pager
    prevHref="/"
    prevTitle="Me"
    nextHref="/inspiration"
    nextTitle="Inspiration"
  />
</Layout>
